text: Walton County is a county in the U.S. state of Georgia. As of the 2020 census, 96,673 people lived there. The county seat is Monroe. It is part of the Atlanta-Sandy Springs-Roswell, GA Metropolitan Statistical Area. ==References== Category:1818 establishments in Georgia (U.S. state) Category:Georgia (U.S. state) counties
title: Walton County, Georgia
